<b>Diakonos</b> is a customizable, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../276/288276.xml">
usable</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../689/423689.xml">
curses</link>-based (console-based, or text-based) <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../310/30310.xml">
text editor</link>.  It was developed with the intention of being easier to configure and use than <skilled_worker wordnetid="110605985" confidence="0.8">
<physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
